p.m.; (box) KPFA, 94.1 FM Live coverage begins at 6:30 a.m.; TELEVISION; (box)
C-SPAN Live coverage begins at 7 a.m.; repeated at 5 p.m.; (box) CNN
Intermittent coverage.  
